===================================================================
--- trunk.orig/vsftpd.conf.5	2014-10-06 10:36:01.173748064 +0200
+++ trunk/vsftpd.conf.5	2014-10-06 10:36:01.169748000 +0200
@@ -84,7 +84,7 @@
 .BR anonymous
 are recognised as anonymous logins.
 
-Default: YES
+Default: NO
 .TP
 .B ascii_download_enable
 When enabled, ASCII mode data transfers will be honoured on downloads.
